  "show": {
    "date": "1989-01-20",
    "comments": [
      "Information of tracklisting from Hal C F Astell's website. He says: \"New session by Dave Sharma, to be re-broadcast on 12 May 1989. It seems that his surname changed to Sharman later on, so later releases of this music carried that 'n' on the end of his name. Tommy mentions that he'll be going to the Marquee during the following week for its 30th Anniversary party. Apparently I don't have a 31 Dec 1988 show Hal means 30 December 1988. because I wiped over it with this show.\"",
      "Tommy tries to help his session artist by getting him two new band members (and inadvertently sacking his drummer...)"
    ]
  },
  "sessions": [
    {
      "artist": "Dave Sharma",
      "details": "one and only. Recorded: 1988-11-25. Available at Live At The BBC (download only)."
    }
